@startuml
title Viaverse Quote / Offer — Activity Diagram
start
:Worker opens matched request detail;
:Validate eligibility\ncapability / risk / request status;
if (Allowed to quote?) then (yes)
  :Create quote draft;
  :Set price and currency;
  :Set schedule / duration;
  :Write offer message;
  :Confirm quote summary;
  :Persist SENT quote and outbox event;
  :Notify requester;
  :Requester compares offers;
  if (Requester accepts?) then (yes)
    :Set quote ACCEPTED;
    :Create Job draft;
    :Next part: Payment session;
  else (no)
    :Quote rejected / ignored;
  endif
else (no)
  :Show blocked reason;
endif
stop

note bottom
Accepting a quote is the boundary between offer flow and payment/job flow.
Quote acceptance must be idempotent.
end note
@enduml
